        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="day02作业"><a href="#day02作业" class="headerlink" title="day02作业"></a>day02作业</h1><ol><li><p>判断一个整数，属于哪个范围：大于0；小于0；等于0</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> num = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入一个整数：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入分数，判定成绩等级(if和switch两种写法)：0<del>59不及格 60</del>69及格 70<del>79丙 80</del>89乙 90~100甲</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> score = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;输入分数：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>开发一款软件，根据公式（身高-108）*2&#x3D;体重，可以有10斤左右的浮动。来观察测试者体重是否合适</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> height = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入身高：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> weight = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入体重：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开发一款软件，根据公式（身高-108）*2&#x3D;体重，可以有10斤左右的浮动。来观察测试者体重是否合适</p></li><li><p>判断一个整数是偶数还是奇数，并输出判断结果</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> num = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入一个整数：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入月份，显示当月的天数   要求：利用case穿透简化代码</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> month = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入月份：&quot;</span>);<span class="keyword">var</span> month = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入月份：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>根据一个数字日期，判断这个日期是这一年的第几天 例如： 20160211，计算后结果为42</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> date = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入数字日期：&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入3个数a,b,c；输出最大的数；</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> a = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入a：&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">    b = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入b：&#x27;</span>),</span><br><span class="line">    c = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入c：&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入一个三位数，如果是水仙花数，输出YES，否则的话，输出NO;所谓的水仙花数是指 每一位的数字立方和等于这位数本身。例如<br>$$<br>153 &#x3D; 1^3 + 5^3 + 3^3<br>$$</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> num = <span class="title function_">prompt</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入三位正数：&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>小明学习js用了7896709887秒。问：共多少天，多少小时，多少分钟，多少秒？</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
